|    101 |   10001 | 2023-01-03 |
|    102 |   10002 | 2023-05-09 |
|    103 |   10003 | 2024-02-20 |
|    104 |   10004 | 2024-06-25 |
|    105 |   10005 | 2024-12-15 |
+--------+---------+------------+
5 rows in set (0.02 sec)

mysql> select * from Customer;
